  "description": "Captions: English\n\nThat’s what we’re searching for—the imperfect is searching for the Perfect. We’re searching for the Ideal. We’re searching for the Absolute. That is what life is. That is what existence is actually. It’s not a religion, a religious thing, a religious idea. It’s Reality.\n\nHelp us caption and translate this video on Amara.org\n\n“Beauty Over Power” is a TheoPhilosophical talk show featuring Bhakti Sudhir Goswami. 21st Century Theism. www.youtube.com/BeautyOverPower\nwww.soundcloud.com/BeautyOverPower\nwww.instagram.com/BeautyOverPower\nwww.vk.com/bsgoswami\n\nTo view full video please go to GoswamiTV channel: http://youtu.be/de6IPThr03w",
